```javascript
function createScalableFolderStructure() {
  var root = DriveApp.getRootFolder();
  var mainFolder = root.createFolder("Dynamic Display Creative");

  // Create main categories
  var clients = mainFolder.createFolder("Clients");
  var projects = mainFolder.createFolder("Projects");
  var services = mainFolder.createFolder("Services");
  var teams = mainFolder.createFolder("Teams");
  var resources = mainFolder.createFolder("Resources");
  var administration = mainFolder.createFolder("Administration");

  // Clients (example clients)
  var clientList = ["Client 1", "Client 2", "Client 3"];
  clientList.forEach(function(client) {
    var clientFolder = clients.createFolder(client);
    clientFolder.createFolder("Project History");
    clientFolder.createFolder("Contracts");
    clientFolder.createFolder("Communication");
  });

  // Projects
  var activeProjects = projects.createFolder("Active Projects");
  projects.createFolder("Completed Projects");
  projects.createFolder("Project Templates");

  // Example active projects
  var projectList = ["Project 1", "Project 2", "Project 3"];
  projectList.forEach(function(project) {
    var projectFolder = activeProjects.createFolder(project);
    projectFolder.createFolder("Project Files");
    projectFolder.createFolder("Client Assets");
    projectFolder.createFolder("Designs");
    projectFolder.createFolder("Team Assignments");
  });

  // Services
  var serviceTypes = ["Construction", "Consultation", "Rental", "Design"];
  serviceTypes.forEach(function(service) {
    services.createFolder(service);
  });

  // Teams (example teams)
  var teamList = ["Team 1", "Team 2", "Team 3"];
  teamList.forEach(function(team) {
    var teamFolder = teams.createFolder(team);
    teamFolder.createFolder("Team Projects");
    teamFolder.createFolder("Team Resources");
    teamFolder.createFolder("Team Communication");
  });

  // Resources
  resources.createFolder("Equipment Inventory");
  var designAssets = resources.createFolder("Design Assets");
  resources.createFolder("Documentation");

  // Design Assets subfolders
  designAssets.createFolder("3D Models");
  designAssets.createFolder("Material Library");
  designAssets.createFolder("Design Templates");

  // Administration
  var hr = administration.createFolder("Human Resources");
  administration.createFolder("Finance");
  administration.createFolder("Legal");

  // HR subfolders
  hr.createFolder("Employee Records");
  hr.createFolder("Policies");
  hr.createFolder("Training Materials");

  Logger.log("Scalable folder structure created successfully!");
}

// Function to add a new client
function addNewClient(clientName) {
  var mainFolder = DriveApp.getFoldersByName("Dynamic Display Creative").next();
  var clientsFolder = mainFolder.getFoldersByName("Clients").next();

  var newClientFolder = clientsFolder.createFolder(clientName);
  newClientFolder.createFolder("Project History");
  newClientFolder.createFolder("Contracts");
  newClientFolder.createFolder("Communication");

  Logger.log("New client folder created for: " + clientName);
}

// Function to add a new team
function addNewTeam(teamName) {
  var mainFolder = DriveApp.getFoldersByName("Dynamic Display Creative").next();
  var teamsFolder = mainFolder.getFoldersByName("Teams").next();

  var newTeamFolder = teamsFolder.createFolder(teamName);
  newTeamFolder.createFolder("Team Projects");
  newTeamFolder.createFolder("Team Resources");
  newTeamFolder.createFolder("Team Communication");

  Logger.log("New team folder created for: " + teamName);
}

// Function to add a new active project
function addNewProject(projectName) {
  var mainFolder = DriveApp.getFoldersByName("Dynamic Display Creative").next();
  var projectsFolder = mainFolder.getFoldersByName("Projects").next();
  var activeProjectsFolder = projectsFolder.getFoldersByName("Active Projects").next();

  var newProjectFolder = activeProjectsFolder.createFolder(projectName);
  newProjectFolder.createFolder("Project Files");
  newProjectFolder.createFolder("Client Assets");
  newProjectFolder.createFolder("Designs");
  newProjectFolder.createFolder("Team Assignments");

  Logger.log("New project folder created for: " + projectName);
}
```

I've updated the Google Apps Script to create the new, more scalable folder structure. Here's an overview of the changes and new features:

1. The main `createScalableFolderStructure()` function creates the basic structure with example clients, projects, and teams.

2. Three new functions have been added to allow for easy expansion of the structure:
   - `addNewClient(clientName)`: Creates a new client folder with appropriate subfolders.
   - `addNewTeam(teamName)`: Creates a new team folder with appropriate subfolders.
   - `addNewProject(projectName)`: Creates a new project folder within the Active Projects folder.

To use this script:

1. Follow the same steps as before to open Google Apps Script in your Google Drive.
2. Replace the existing code with this new script.
3. Save the project.
4. Run the `createScalableFolderStructure()` function to create the initial structure.

After the initial structure is created, you can use the additional functions to add new clients, teams, or projects as needed. To do this:

1. In the Google Apps Script editor, select the function you want to run (e.g., `addNewClient`) from the dropdown menu next to the "Run" button.
2. Click "Run".
3. When prompted, enter the name of the new client, team, or project in the pop-up dialog.

This setup allows you to easily expand your folder structure as your company grows, without having to manually create new folders each time.

Remember, you'll need to grant the necessary permissions the first time you run each function.

